OL,5, Survivors of the Grenfell Tower fire   
OL,6, and government minister Michael Gove   
OL,7, have criticised Formula 1 team Mercedes
OL,8, for signing a deal with a firm linked  
OL,9, to the tower.                          
OL,11,FThe F1 team signed a deal with         
OL,12,FKingspan, which made some of the       
OL,13,Finsulation used in the cladding.       
OL,15,FGrenfell survivors called the          
OL,16,Fsponsorship "truly shocking", while Mr 
OL,17,FGove said he was "deeply disappointed".
OL,19,FKingspan said it played no role in the 
OL,20,Fdesign of the cladding on the tower.   
